<div id="con-white" class="panel" data-color="about">    <div id="con-white-about"  class="con-white">        <div id="con-white-about-img"  class="con-white">            <img src="img/robertpiano.png" alt="Robert Koziel">        </div>        <div id="con-white-about-text"  class="con-white">            <div id="con-about-text-title">                <p id="con-about-text-title-about">                    About                </p>                <p id="con-about-text-title-name">                    Robert Koziel                </p>            </div>            <p>                I have always believed from a young age that music must come straight                from the heart with pure intentions. Creating my music, I feel nothing                but the purest connection with the highest power. Every tone in my music                reflects my life experiences and is a clear message to everyone.            </p>        </div>    </div></div>